<h2 id="product">Product Managers</h2>
<p>Ensure your products are being built to brand, accessibility and development standards.</p>
<p>The Design System:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Speeds up your design process</li>
    <li>Takes the burden of accessibility compliance off you (WCAG 2.1 AA)</li>
    <li>Ensures you're following NSW Government branding</li>
    <li>Enables your designers and developers working off a common base</li>
</ul>
<p>Our pre-built kits:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Make your digital products responsive for mobile, tablet, and computers</li>
    <li>Dramatically speed up your development process</li>
    <li>Allows you to share components with teams who also used the Design System</li>
</ul>


<h2 id="designers">Designers</h2>
<p>Ideate and prototype faster with pre-built, accessible and tested assets. </p>
<p>The Design System:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Provides single source of truth for all Digital Brand assets</li>
    <li>Contains detailed component and pattern UX guidance </li>
    <li>Connects you with a digital community for support and sharing</li>
</ul>
<p>Our Figma kit:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Includes 30+ reusable components styled to responsive breakpoints</li>
    <li>Meets brand and accessibility compliance (WCAG 2.1 AA)</li>
    <li>Provides state, colour, and content type variants</li>
    <li>Features reusable page layout templates</li>
    <li>Ensures consistecy between design and code</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="developers">Developers</h2>
<p>Build more in less time with flexible and scalable pre-built solutions. </p>
<p>The Design System:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Has mulitple Dev toolkits</li>
    <li>Package Management</li>
    <li>Changelog and versioning</li>
    <li>Provides comprehensive documentation</li>
    <li>Automated release pipeline</li>
    <li>Uses semantic versioning with most releases being backwards compatible</li>
</ul>
<p>Our code kits:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Include 30+ reusable components plus core and helper classes</li>
    <li>Meets brand and accessibility compliance (WCAG 2.1 AA)</li>
    <li>Ensures cross-browser and cross device compatibility</li>
    <li>Built using modular (BEM), clean and reusable code</li>
</ul>


